    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>See <a href="http://octopress.org/docs/blogging/code/">Sharing Code Snippets</a></p>

<h3>Syntax</h3>

<pre><code>``` [language] [title] [url] [link text] [linenos:false] [start:#] [mark:#,#-#]
code snippet
```
</code></pre>

<p>a ruby example</p>

<pre><code>``` ruby a ruby example
require 'redcarpet'
markdown = Redcarpet.new("Hello World!")
puts markdown.to_html
```
</code></pre>

